The properties, in order, before the JSON Schema document, embedded into the [=JSON Schema=] are as follows:

1. [=type=]

1. [=modelVersion=]

1. [=id=]

1. [=schemaVersion=]

1. [=name=]

1. [=author=]

1. [=authored=]

